high_descs: Turn around and walk to the diningtable.
Take the spatula from the table.
Put the steel spatula clean into the washing basin.
Take the steel spoon from the diningtable and turn around it.
Put the spatula into the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula, clean it and put it on the dining table.

high_descs: Go straight turn left to reach the diningtable.
Pick the spatula from the table.
Turn left go straight and turn right to reach the sink.
Put the spatula into the sink and pour the water and clean it.
walk back and head to the diningtable.
Put the cleaned spatula on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned spatula on the diningtable.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left twice until you are in front of a white dining table in front of a couch.
Pick up the spatula on the left with the handle facing the couch.
Turn left and walk to forward, then left and right until you are facing the sink.
Place the spatula on the left side of the sink, turn on the water, clean it off then pick it up.
Turn right, left and walk forward then forward and left to face the dining room table again.
Place the clean spatula on the upper left corner of the dining room table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the dining room table.
